{
  "schema_version": "2.0",
  "name": "relationship",
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "type": "gameplay",
  "required": false,
  "description": "NPC relationship tracking plugin with relationship change blocks and context injection.",
  "dependencies": ["character", "database", "core-blocks"],
  "prompt": {
    "position": "character",
    "priority": 48,
    "template": "prompts/relationship-context.md"
  },
  "capabilities": {},
  "blocks": {
    "relationship_change": {
      "instruction": "当 NPC 与玩家的关系发生显著变化时（好感提升/降低、关系类型转变），在回复末尾附加：\n```json:relationship_change\n{\"npc_name\": \"NPC名\", \"change\": 10, \"reason\": \"变化原因\", \"new_level\": 60, \"rank\": \"友好\", \"relationship_type\": \"friend\"}\n```\n规则：\n- change 为正数表示好感提升，负数表示下降\n- new_level 为变化后的总好感值（0-100）\n- rank 必须为以下之一：亲密/友好/中立/冷淡/敌对\n- relationship_type 必须为以下之一：friend/rival/romantic/mentor/enemy\n- 仅在关系确实发生变化时输出，不要每回合都输出",
      "schema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "npc_name": { "type": "string" },
          "change": { "type": "number" },
          "reason": { "type": "string" },
          "new_level": { "type": "number" },
          "rank": { "type": "string" },
          "relationship_type": { "type": "string" }
        },
        "required": ["npc_name", "change", "reason", "new_level", "rank", "relationship_type"]
      },
      "handler": {
        "actions": [
          { "type": "storage_write", "key": "npc-relationships" },
          { "type": "emit_event", "event": "relationship-changed" }
        ]
      },
      "ui": {
        "component": "custom",
        "renderer_name": "relationship_change"
      },
      "requires_response": false
    }
  },
  "events": {
    "emit": ["relationship-changed"],
    "listen": []
  },
  "storage": {
    "keys": ["npc-relationships"]
  },
  "permissions": {},
  "extensions": {
    "runtime_settings": {
      "settings": [
        {
          "key": "relationship_depth",
          "type": "enum",
          "label": "Relationship Depth",
          "description": "Level of detail in relationship tracking.",
          "default": "rich",
          "options": [
            {
              "value": "simple",
              "label": "Simple",
              "i18n": { "zh": { "label": "简洁" } }
            },
            {
              "value": "rich",
              "label": "Rich",
              "i18n": { "zh": { "label": "丰富" } }
            }
          ],
          "affects": ["story"],
          "i18n": {
            "zh": {
              "label": "关系深度",
              "description": "关系追踪的详细程度。"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "i18n": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Relationship",
      "description": "Track NPC relationships with the player, including affinity levels and relationship types."
    },
    "zh": {
      "name": "NPC 关系",
      "description": "追踪 NPC 与玩家的关系变化，包括好感度与关系类型。"
    }
  }
}
